Package: shitty
Architecture: any
Depends:
 shitty-terminfo,
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python3:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Recommends:
 shitty-doc,
# To play the "beep" sound for the terminal
 libcanberra0
Suggests:
# For tui shitten
 imagemagick
Provides:
 x-terminal-emulator
Description: fast, featureful, GPU based terminal emulator
 shitty supports modern terminal features like: graphics, unicode,
 true-color, OpenType ligatures, mouse protocol, focus tracking, and
 bracketed paste.
 .
 shitty has a framework for "shittens", small terminal programs that can be used
 to extend its functionality.

Package: shitty-terminfo
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: fast, featureful, GPU based terminal emulator (terminfo file)
 This package provides the xterm-shitty terminfo definition for the shitty
 terminal emulator so that it can easily be installed on remote systems.

Package: shitty-doc
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Section: doc
Built-Using:
 ${sphinxdoc:Built-Using},
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${sphinxdoc:Depends},
Breaks: shitty (<< 0.9.1-1~)
Replaces: shitty (<< 0.9.1-1~)
Description: fast, featureful, GPU based terminal emulator (documentation)
 This package contains the AsciiDoc/HTML documentation for the shitty terminal
 emulator.
